org.apache.flink.types

类 ListValue<V extends Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.types.ListValue<V>
  • 类型参数:
    V - Type of the list elements.
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<V>, java.util.Collection<V>, java.util.List<V>, IOReadableWritable, Value

    @Public
public abstract class ListValue<V extends Value>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Value, java.util.List<V>
    Generic list base type for PACT programs that implements the Value and List interfaces. PactList encapsulates a Java ArrayList object.
    另请参阅:
    Value, List, ArrayList, 序列化表格
